
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Private_Limited_Company";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}
<div class="container-fluid mt-4">
    <div class="col-12 card mt-3">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-9 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <div class="jumbotron-fluid bg-light card">
                    <h4 class="card-header  text-center bg-info text-white" style="font-size:22px;">
                        PRIVATE LIMITED COMPANY
                    </h4>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                                <img src="~/Content/images/private.jpg" class="img-fluid img-thumbnail"  style="max-height:320px;min-height:300px;" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                                <div class="text-justify" style="font-size:18px;">
                                    A Private Limited Company is a separate legal entity both in terms of taxation as well as liability. We need two or more persons but not more than 200 persons, for incorporation of Private Company. Right of shareholder is restricted to transfer their shares and they do not invite public to subscribe to its share capital. Now limit of capital has deleted under companies act, 2013. No such requirement of minimum paid up capital..

                                </div>
                                
                            </div>


                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <br />
                    
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 float-right">
                @Html.Partial("_EnquiryView")
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="clearfix"></div>
<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12  card">
    
        <div class="card-header bg-info text-white ">
            <h5 class="text-left" style="font-size:21px;">Process</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            @*<div class="text-justify">
                    A simple procedure is followed for getting a firm registered.
                </div>*@
            <ol type="1" style="font-size:18px;">

                <li>Application for name approval.</li>
                <li>Obtain Digital Signature Certificate.</li>
                <li>Drafting of MOA / AOA, other documents.</li>
                <li>Preparation of INC-9, DIR-2, Affidavit and other documents.</li>
                <li>Incorporation documents will be filed on MCA Portal</li>
                <li>Get Certificate of Incorporation</li>

            </ol>

        </div>
</div>


    <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12  card">
        <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
            <h5 class="text-left" style="font-size:21px;"> Required Documents</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <ol style="font-size:18px;">
                <li>Passport size color photograph of each subscribers</li>
                <li>Copy of PAN card (Passport in case of NRI) of each subscriber. </li>
                <li>Copy of address proof of each subscriber ( Bank Statement, telephone bill, electricity bill, mobile bill not older 2 months) </li>
                <li>Self attested copy of identity proof of each subscriber (Voters ID, Passport, Driving License, Adhar card)  </li>
                <li>Address proof for Registered Office of the Company.(any utility bill, rent agreement, NOC from owner)  </li>
                <li>Digital Signature Certificate (DSC)    </li>
                <li>Main object of Company   </li>

            </ol>


        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12  card">
        <div class="row bg-secondary text-white p-3 rounded" style="font-size:18px;">
            <p class="text-justify">WMC is the best consultancy services platform in India, offering a various kind of services like to start a business and manage business such as Incorporation of Company, LLP, Registration of Partnership Firm etc. and trademark filing, tax registration, tax filing and GST registration and their filing. </p>
            <p class="text-justify">WMC can help you to register or Incorporation of Private Company. The average time taken to draft and file registration or Incorporation of Private Company is about 5 - 10 working days, subject to government processing time and client document submission. Get a free consultation to register or Incorporation of Private Company by scheduling an appointment with a WMC Advisor .</p>
        </div>
</div>
